Uses of Package
org.vast.sensorML

  • Packages that use org.vast.sensorML 
    Package Description
    org.vast.sensorML  
  • Classes in org.vast.sensorML used by org.vast.sensorML 
    Class and Description
    AbstractProcessImpl
    This class implements both AbstractProcess from SensorML v2.0 bindings and IProcessExec to allow execution if an executable implementation is provided.
    In order to provide execution capabilitiy, this class can wrap an implementation of IProcessExec corresponding to a particular algorithm.
    AggregateProcessImpl
    POJO class for XML type AggregateProcessType(@http://www.opengis.net/sensorml/2.0).
    ExecutableProcessImpl
    Abstract base for all executable process implementations.
    This class provides logic to run a process synchronously by simply calling ExecutableProcessImpl.execute() or in its own thread using ExecutableProcessImpl.start() and ExecutableProcessImpl.stop().
    ProcessLoader
    This class loads the right process based on the method URI provided in the SensorML description.
    SMLFactory
